text: Jennifer Ann Agutter (born 20 December 1952) is a British actress. She was born in Taunton, Somerset. She starred in The Railway Children, Walkabout, Logan's Run and An American Werewolf in London. ==References== == Other websites == * Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Somerset Category:BAFTA Award winning actors Category:British child actors Category:Emmy Award winning actors Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors
